Package com.djrapitops.plan.command.commands.manage

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ManageBackupCommand
    This command is used to backup a database to a .db file.
    ManageClearCommand
    This manage SubCommand is used to clear a database of all data.
    ManageConDebugCommand
    This manage SubCommand is used to request settings from Bungee so that connection can be established.
    ManageDisableCommand
    This manage SubCommand is used to disable some features of the plugin temporarily.
    ManageExportCommand
    This manage SubCommand is used to import data from 3rd party plugins.
    ManageHotSwapCommand
    This manage SubCommand is used to swap to a different database and reload the plugin if the connection to the new database can be established.
    ManageImportCommand
    This manage SubCommand is used to import data from 3rd party plugins.
    ManageMoveCommand
    This manage SubCommand is used to move all data from one database to another.
    ManageRawDataCommand
    This manage subcommand is used to remove a single player's data from the database.
    ManageRemoveCommand
    This manage subcommand is used to remove a single player's data from the dbSystem.
    ManageRestoreCommand
    This manage SubCommand is used to restore a backup.db file in the /plugins/Plan folder.
    ManageSetupCommand
    This manage SubCommand is used to request settings from Bungee so that connection can be established.
    ManageUninstalledCommand
    This SubCommand is used to set a server as uninstalled on Plan.
